 that cost. For example, if you cast Chord of Calling (a spell with convoke and mana cost {X}{G}{G}{G}) and choose X to be 3, the total cost is {3}{G}{G}{G}. If you tap two green creatures and two red creatures, you’ll have to pay {1}{G}.£7/18/2014: If a creature you control has a mana ability with {T} in the cost, activating that ability while casting a spell with convoke will result in the creature being tapped when you pay the spell’s costs. You won’t be able to tap it again for convoke. Similarly, if you sacrifice a creature to activate a mana ability while casting a spell with convoke, that creature won’t be on the battlefield when you pay the spell’s costs, so you won’t be able to tap it for convoke.','G',NULL,'0.01','0.17','0.94',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','鼓舞勇气',NULL,'Rassembler son courage','Mut ansammeln','Raccogliere il Coraggio','かき集める勇気','Concentração de Coragem','Набраться мужества','Armarse de valor',NULL,'瞬间',NULL,'Éphémère','Spontanzauber','Istantaneo','インスタント','Mágica Instantânea','Мгновенное заклинание','Instantáneo',NULL,'召集（使用此咒语时，你每为它横置一个生物，便可以少支付{1}，或一点所横置生物颜色的法术力。）£目标生物得+2/+2直到回合结束。',NULL,'Convocation #_(Chaque créature que vous engagez en jouant ce sort réduit son coût de {1} ou d''un mana de la couleur de cette créature.)_#£La créature ciblée gagne +2/+2 jusqu''à la fin du tour.','Einberufen #_(Jede Kreatur, die du tappst, während du diesen Zauberspruch spielst, reduziert dessen Kosten um {1} oder um ein Mana der Farbe jener Kreatur.)_#£Eine Kreatur deiner Wahl erhält +2/+2 bis zum Ende des Zuges.','Convocazione #_(Ciascuna creatura che TAPpi mentre giochi questa magia riduce il suo costo di {1} o di un mana del colore di quella creatura.)_#£La creatura bersaglio prende +2/+2 fino alla fine del turno.','召集 （あなたがこの呪文をプレイする段階であなたがタップした各クリーチャーにつき、この呪文のコストはそのクリーチャーの色のマナ１点か{1}少なくなる。）£クリーチャー１体を対象とする。それはターン終了時まで＋２/＋２の修整を受ける。','Convocar #_(Cada criatura que você vira ao jogar esta mágica reduz seu custo em {1} ou em um mana da cor daquela criatura.)_#